  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Problem in providing treatment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Government Medical Officers' Association said treatments were limited to essential services in hospitals across the country due to the fuel crisis.",
        "The association also announced that it would be impossible to run surgeries and outpatient units if health workers were not provided with fuel or proper transportation facilities next week.",
        "Health services in the country are in a critical condition due to the fuel crisis and drug shortages.",
        "Representatives of the Central Committee of the Government Medical Officers' Association and 31 branches of the Association met today (26) to discuss the matter.",
        "It was discussed at the meeting that if the fuel supply system is not implemented giving priority to the health service, it will not be possible to perform the duties properly.",
        "It is learned that the matter will be discussed with the Health Minister tomorrow (28)."
      ],
